### Search Categories by Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin/search?name=electronics
Accept: application/json

###

### Search Categories - Partial match
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin/search?name=sport
Accept: application/json

###

### Search Categories - Case insensitive
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin/search?name=FASHION
Accept: application/json

###

### Search Categories - No results
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin/search?name=zzznomatch
Accept: application/json
